		<body>
			<div type="transcription">
				<div type="original">
					<p>The original transcription is not available.</p>
				</div>
				<div type="translation">
					<p>From: Consul <persName ref="#ehri_dr_yamaguchi">Yamaguchi</persName> (<placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/2761369/vienna.html">Vienna</placeName>)</p>
					<p>To: Foreign Minister <persName ref="#ehri_dr_mamoru_shigemitsu">Shigemitsu Mamoru</persName> (<placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/1850147/tokyo.html">Tokyo</placeName>)</p>
					<p>
						<date when="1944-02-29">Since 29</date>th of last month, the control of <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-864" type="subject">Jews</term> in <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/2761369/vienna.html">Vienna</placeName> has become even harsher. </p>
					<p> The following is what we learned in extreme confidentiality. Those who <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-582" type="subject">married Jews</term> are confined to<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-553" type="subject">
							certain houses</term>; Those with <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-374" type="subject">mixed Jewish blood</term> are not allowed to join the <orgName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/authorities/ehri_cb-388">Arbeitsfront</orgName> or are
							<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-332" type="subject">expelled</term> from it.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
